A blueskinned mastery chroma for Varus would make my year, as far as LoL.
{{champion:110}} 

{{sticker:slayer-pantheon-thumbs}} 

No (but also yes), but really, mastery chromas would be awesome! It certainly would give some extra incentive to master characters, and make people wonder what (mystery?) chroma they'd receive with mastery of x character -- which could possibly lead to more drive to buy x, y, or z character?

I dunno. I like it, though!
